## Code Example

```javascript
// Example: deterministic mask preserving format
function maskForColumn(val){ 
  if (val===null) return null;
  const s = String(val);
  const masked = s.replace(/[0-9]/g,'0');
  return masked.length>0 ? masked : val;
}
```

